Short:    HD-Installer for Black Monks "Test Drive 2" Cracktro
Author:   Codetapper/Action (codetapper@hotmail.com), ICQ: 26051687
Uploader: Codetapper/Action (codetapper@hotmail.com)
Version:  1.1
Type:     game/patch

This patch applies to "Test Drive 2 Cracktro" (c) 1989 Black Monks.

REQUIREMENTS:
- Slave requires WHDLoad V13+.
- Game requires 512kb chip mem (+150kb other memory for preload option)

FEATURES:
- Full load from HD
- Keyboard routine added
- Blitter wait added
- Snoop bug fixed
- Copperlist bugs fixed (x2)
- Intro can be compressed to save space (FImp, Propack etc)
- Source: https://github.com/wepl/winstalls
- Quit option (default key is 'F10')

HISTORY:
2024-08-21 Version 1.1 by Wepl
- fixed to work on 68000 (some os left over)

TO DO:
- RomIcon, NewIcon and GlowIcon (created by ???!)

A nice little intro with the music ripped from Hybris!


Codetapper/Action (06-Jan-2002)


